        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p style="text-align:justify;">
            Second Families is a 501(c) (3) nonprofit serving refugee families in Southern California. 
            Founded in 2016, Second Families provides assistance with non-food items (furniture, clothing, 
            school supplies, household goods), as well as opportunities for education and enrichment scholarship.
            Our aim is to connect families to resources that will ease their transition and connect them to new American
            friends, making them feel safe and comfortable in their new home.
        </p>    
